### Authentication
# @name Login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/steam-ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticket": "integration-ticket",
    "useNativeAuth": false
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}

### System Status
GET {{host}}/api/game/system/status
X-Token: {{auth_token}}

### Pause Simulation
POST {{host}}/api/game/system/pause
X-Token: {{auth_token}}

### Resume Simulation
POST {{host}}/api/game/system/resume
X-Token: {{auth_token}}

### Tick Duration (Get)
GET {{host}}/api/game/system/tick
X-Token: {{auth_token}}

### Tick Duration (Set)
POST {{host}}/api/game/system/tick-set
X-Token: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "duration": 750
}

### Broadcast Message
POST {{host}}/api/game/system/message
X-Token: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Server maintenance starting soon."
}
